              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Proton beam with energy of 500 MeV was steered onto",
                "production targets to produce radioactive isotope",
                "21Na. Produced ions were ionized, accelerated off the",
                "source's high-voltage platform at up to 60 kV and",
                "sent through a mass separator to select the ion beam",
                "of 21Na. The beam was transported in the low-energy",
                "beam transport electrostatic beam line and sent via a",
                "switchyard to room-temperature linac"
              ]
            }
          ],
